.fi
.sp
.TP
.B Example Pair with another device
.nf
\fB> pair AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\fP
.fi
.sp
.TP
.B Example Pair with display\-only IO capability
.nf
\fB> pair \-c DisplayOnly 00:11:22:33:44:55\fP
.fi
.sp
.TP
