.TP
.B Example Set another static random address
.nf
\fB> static\-addr D0:11:22:33:44:55\fP
.fi
.sp
.TP
.B Example Set different static address
.nf
\fB> static\-addr E0:AA:BB:CC:DD:EE\fP
.fi
.sp
.UNINDENT
.SS public\-addr
.sp
Set public address
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B Usage
\fB> public\-addr <address>\fP
.TP
.B <address>
Public Bluetooth address to set for the controller
.TP
.B Example Set public Bluetooth address
.nf
\fB> public\-addr 00:11:22:33:44:55\fP
.fi
.sp
.TP
